545
00:28:28,780 --> 00:28:29,659
I want to know your answer.

546
00:28:29,660 --> 00:28:30,860
I can't answer that.

547
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:58,820
I thought we were the same.

548
00:28:59,580 --> 00:29:01,140
You came to Shanghai from Leshan

549
00:29:01,370 --> 00:29:02,619
with your heart set on your career.

550
00:29:02,620 --> 00:29:03,819
So you can understand

551
00:29:03,820 --> 00:29:05,940
my situation and my choice.

552
00:29:06,130 --> 00:29:07,780
Not to mention I'm a man.

553
00:29:10,170 --> 00:29:11,650
You don't understand me.

554
00:29:58,970 --> 00:30:00,929
(You don't want me to work in Singapore)

555
00:30:00,930 --> 00:30:02,209
(or you don't want me to follow you?)

556
00:30:02,210 --> 00:30:04,249
(I don't want you)

557
00:30:04,250 --> 00:30:06,100
(to lose yourself for me.)

558
00:30:07,290 --> 00:30:08,820
(Xue Yuming, I want to ask you.)

559
